def test_camel_to_title_case(capsys):
	"""
	Test the camel_to_title_case function.
	"""
	# Simple test
	camel_to_title_case("ThisIsATestCase")
	out, err = capsys.readouterr()
	assert out == "This Is A Test Case\n"

	# Manually add a dash
	camel_to_title_case("ThisIsATestCaseWithADash", "_", as_list=False)
	out, err = capsys.readouterr()
	assert out == "This_Is_A_Test_Case_With_A_Dash\n"

	# SHOULD fail a not a string test
	camel_to_title_case(123)
	out, err = capsys.readouterr()
	assert out == ""
	assert err == "camel_to_title_case" + "    ! An error has occurred in" + " forcing argument 0 to be a string.\n"


def test_swap_camel_words(capsys):
	"""
	A simple test for the swap_camel_words function.
	"""
	# Simple test for the camel_to_title_case function.
	swap_camel_words("ThisIsATestCase", 1, 3)
	out, err = capsys.readouterr()
	assert out == "ThisTestCaseIsA\n"
